spec_data.Name: psl-make-dafsa
spec_data.Description:
This script produces C/C++ code or an architecture-independent binary object
which represents a Deterministic Acyclic Finite State Automaton (DAFSA)
from a plain text Public Suffix List.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 11 Aug 2017 02:14:14 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Compiles the Public Suffix List into DAFSA form
